01:12:53,411 --> 01:12:55,997
<i>Snowfall, Home Fire đây.</i>

1092
01:12:56,081 --> 01:12:57,290
<i>Nghe rõ trả lời.</i>

1093
01:12:57,874 --> 01:12:59,459
